(136, 1, 'admin/articles', 'POST', '127.0.0.1', '{\"type_id\":\"1\",\"title\":\"Explosion \\u00e0 Goma\\/RDC\",\"sub_title\":\"Explosion \\u00e0 Goma\\/RDC\",\"description\":\"<p style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 1rem;color: rgb(89, 93, 105);font-family: Rubik, sans-serif;font-size: 15px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\\\"><span style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box;font-weight: bolder;font-family: Arial;font-size: 15px\\\">A un moment o\\u00f9 personne ne s\\u2019y attendait, une explosion comme une opportunit\\u00e9 vient de s\\u2019\\u00e9clater \\u00e0 Goma<\\/span><br style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box\\\"\\/><\\/p><p style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 1rem;color: rgb(89, 93, 105);font-family: Rubik, sans-serif;font-size: 15px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\\\"><span style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box;font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;, serif\\\"><span style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box;font-family: Arial\\\">Comme un \\u0153uf, incub\\u00e9 au HUB UN JOUR NOUVEAU en D\\u00e9cembre 2021, l\\u2019\\u00e9closion de CASALIND est une forte explosion des opportunit\\u00e9s pour les jeunes entrepreneurs, les commer\\u00e7ants, les cha\\u00eenes de radios et t\\u00e9l\\u00e9visions et pour la population en g\\u00e9n\\u00e9ral.<\\/span><\\/span><\\/p><p style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 1rem;color: rgb(89, 93, 105);font-family: Rubik, sans-serif;font-size: 15px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\\\"><span style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box;font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;, serif\\\"><span style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box;font-family: Arial\\\">Voici le premier poussin sorti des \\u0153ufs de&nbsp;<\\/span><span style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box;font-weight: bolder\\\"><span style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box;font-family: Arial\\\">CASALIND&nbsp;:<\\/span><\\/span><span style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box;font-family: Arial\\\">&nbsp;<\\/span><span style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box;font-family: Arial\\\">&nbsp;<\\/span><\\/span><\\/p><table cellspacing=\\\"0\\\" cellpadding=\\\"0\\\" width=\\\"606\\\"><tbody style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box;border-style: solid;border-width: 0px\\\"><tr style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box;border-style: solid;border-width: 0px;height: 144px\\\" class=\\\"firstRow\\\"><td width=\\\"182\\\" valign=\\\"top\\\" style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box; border-color: inherit; border-width: 0px; padding: 0px 7px;\\\" height=\\\"144\\\"><p style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box;margin-bottom: 0;line-height: normal\\\"><span style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box;font-family: Arial\\\">&nbsp;<\\/span><\\/p><p style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box;margin-bottom: 0;line-height: normal\\\"><span style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box;font-family: Arial\\\">&nbsp;<\\/span><\\/p><p style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box;margin-bottom: 0;line-height: normal\\\"><span style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box;font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;, serif\\\"><img src=\\\"http:\\/\\/localhost:8000\\/storage\\/uploads\\/image\\/2022\\/07\\/14\\/eci.png\\\" title=\\\"\\/uploads\\/image\\/2022\\/07\\/14\\/eci.png\\\" alt=\\\"eci.png\\\"\\/><\\/span><\\/p><\\/td><td width=\\\"423\\\" valign=\\\"top\\\" style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box; border-color: inherit; border-width: 0px; padding: 0px 7px;\\\" height=\\\"144\\\"><p style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box;margin-bottom: 0;line-height: normal\\\"><span style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 13px;font-family: Arial\\\">CASALIND NEWS est une plateforme de m\\u00e9dias et de promotion des startups et entreprises mettant en ligne les cha\\u00eenes de radios et des t\\u00e9l\\u00e9visions pour \\u00eatre suivies partout dans le monde entier.<\\/span><\\/p><p style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box;margin-bottom: 0;line-height: normal\\\"><span style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 13px;font-family: Arial\\\">&nbsp;<\\/span><\\/p><p style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box;margin-bottom: 11px;line-height: normal\\\"><span style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 14px;font-family: Symbol\\\"><span style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box;font-family: Arial\\\">\\u00b7<\\/span><span style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box;font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 9px;line-height: normal;font-family: Arial\\\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<\\/span><\\/span><em style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box\\\"><span style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 14px;font-family: Nunito\\\"><span style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box;font-family: Arial\\\">Permettre aux radios et aux t\\u00e9l\\u00e9visions m\\u00eame celle ayant la fr\\u00e9quence la plus m\\u00e9diocre d&#39;\\u00eatre suivies partout dans le monde entier ;<\\/span><\\/span><\\/em><\\/p><p style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box;margin-bottom: 11px;line-height: normal\\\"><span style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 14px;font-family: Symbol\\\"><span style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box;font-family: Arial\\\">\\u00b7<\\/span><span style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box;font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 9px;line-height: normal;font-family: Arial\\\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<\\/span><\\/span><em style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box\\\"><span style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 14px;font-family: Nunito\\\"><span style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box;font-family: Arial\\\">Application du marketing digital le plus productif pour promouvoir les startups et les entreprises ;<\\/span><\\/span><\\/em><\\/p><p style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box;margin-bottom: 11px;line-height: normal\\\"><span style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 14px;font-family: Symbol\\\"><span style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box;font-family: Arial\\\">\\u00b7<\\/span><span style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box;font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 9px;line-height: normal;font-family: Arial\\\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<\\/span><\\/span><em style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box\\\"><span style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 14px;font-family: Nunito\\\"><span style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box;font-family: Arial\\\">Une plateforme de m\\u00e9dia avec des fonctionnalit\\u00e9s permettant \\u00e0 tout utilisateur de s&#39;occuper \\u00e9conomiquement en vaquant \\u00e0 ses autres occupations ;<\\/span><\\/span><\\/em><\\/p><p style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box;margin-bottom: 0;line-height: normal\\\"><span style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box;font-family: Arial\\\">&nbsp;<\\/span><\\/p><\\/td><\\/tr><\\/tbody><\\/table><p style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 1rem;color: rgb(89, 93, 105);font-family: Rubik, sans-serif;font-size: 15px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\\\"><span style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box;font-weight: bolder\\\"><span style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box;font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;, serif\\\"><span style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box;font-family: Arial\\\">VOS FARDEAUX SONT \\u00d4TES<\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/p><p style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 1rem;color: rgb(89, 93, 105);font-family: Rubik, sans-serif;font-size: 15px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\\\"><span style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box;font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;, serif\\\"><span style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box;font-family: Arial\\\">Lors de l\\u2019interview, mademoiselle Judith KABANO, directrice administrative de Casalind explique comment Casalind News est un sauveur des entreprises et startups en voie de disparition et une m\\u00e8re pour les MPME&nbsp;:<\\/span><\\/span><\\/p><p style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 1rem;color: rgb(89, 93, 105);font-family: Rubik, sans-serif;font-size: 15px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\\\"><span style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box;font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;, serif\\\"><span style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box;font-family: Arial\\\">\\u00ab&nbsp;Lorsqu\\u2019on pose la question de savoir pourquoi les entreprises qui ferment sont tomb\\u00e9es en faillite on a toujours des r\\u00e9ponses qui renvoient vers le probl\\u00e8me de vente. Si une entreprise ne sait pas vendre elle n\\u2019existera jamais.<\\/span><\\/span><\\/p><p style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 1rem;color: rgb(89, 93, 105);font-family: Rubik, sans-serif;font-size: 15px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\\\"><span style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box;font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;, serif\\\"><span style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box;font-family: Arial\\\">Plusieurs startups se trompent de strat\\u00e9gie marketing et c\\u2019est l\\u00e0 que commence l\\u2019\\u00e9chec. Si vous basez votre marketing sur la publicit\\u00e9 seulement soyez s\\u00fbrs que vous avez d\\u00e9j\\u00e0 \\u00e9chou\\u00e9.<\\/span><\\/span><\\/p><p style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 1rem;color: rgb(89, 93, 105);font-family: Rubik, sans-serif;font-size: 15px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\\\"><span style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box;font-weight: bolder\\\"><span style=\\\"box-sizing: border-boxtext-decoration:underline;\\\"><span style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box;font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;, serif\\\"><span style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box;font-family: Arial\\\">Retenez ceci&nbsp;:<\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/p><p style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 1rem;color: rgb(89, 93, 105);font-family: Rubik, sans-serif;font-size: 15px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);margin-left: 52px\\\"><span style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box;font-family: Symbol\\\"><span style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box;font-family: Arial\\\">\\u00b7<\\/span><span style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box;font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 9px;line-height: normal;font-family: Arial\\\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<\\/span><\\/span><span style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box;font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;, serif\\\"><span style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box;font-family: Arial\\\">Les gens n\\u2019ont pas besoin que vous leur dites que vous \\u00eates professionnels, ils veulent d\\u00e9couvrir que vous l\\u2019\\u00eates&nbsp;;<\\/span><\\/span><\\/p><p style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 1rem;color: rgb(89, 93, 105);font-family: Rubik, sans-serif;font-size: 15px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);margin-left: 52px\\\"><span style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box;font-family: Symbol\\\"><span style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box;font-family: Arial\\\">\\u00b7<\\/span><span style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box;font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 9px;line-height: normal;font-family: Arial\\\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<\\/span><\\/span><span style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box;font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;, serif\\\"><span style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box;font-family: Arial\\\">Les gens n\\u2019ont pas besoin que vous leur dites qu\\u2019ils ont besoin de votre service ou votre produit, ils ont besoin de sentir le besoin et d\\u00e9couvrir que leur progression ou leur survie en d\\u00e9pend<\\/span><\\/span><\\/p><p style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 1rem;color: rgb(89, 93, 105);font-family: Rubik, sans-serif;font-size: 15px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);margin-left: 52px\\\"><span style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box;font-family: Symbol\\\"><span style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box;font-family: Arial\\\">\\u00b7<\\/span><span style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box;font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 9px;line-height: normal;font-family: Arial\\\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<\\/span><\\/span><span style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box;font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;, serif\\\"><span style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box;font-family: Arial\\\">Au fait, les gens n\\u2019ont pas besoin d\\u2019\\u00e9couter de vous que\\u2026 Ils ont besoin de sentir de vous que\\u2026 pour acheter vos services ou vos produits<\\/span><\\/span><\\/p><p style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 1rem;color: rgb(89, 93, 105);font-family: Rubik, sans-serif;font-size: 15px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\\\"><span style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box;font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;, serif\\\"><span style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box;font-family: Arial\\\">Casalind News vient porter vos stress, vous d\\u00e9charger de ce grand fardeau de vente.<\\/span><\\/span><\\/p><p style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 1rem;color: rgb(89, 93, 105);font-family: Rubik, sans-serif;font-size: 15px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\\\"><span style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box;font-weight: bolder\\\"><span style=\\\"box-sizing: border-boxtext-decoration:underline;\\\"><span style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box;font-family: Arial\\\">Retenez encore ceci&nbsp;:<\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><span style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box;font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;, serif\\\"><span style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box;font-family: Arial\\\">&nbsp;Le client est la source de toute r\\u00e9ussite d\\u2019une entreprise. Le plus grand d\\u00e9fi pour cette derni\\u00e8re est d\\u2019aborder les gens et le transformer en client car il est toujours difficile de faire acheter un produit ou un service nouveau \\u00e0 quelqu\\u2019un.<\\/span><\\/span><\\/p><p style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 1rem;color: rgb(89, 93, 105);font-fa